data.description:
Seller is offering $3000.00 Buyer incentive for closing costs or paying down your interest rate!
Looking for a move in ready home that's easy to maintain This is it. Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring in living areas and all bedrooms, Ceramic Tile in baths, New Carpet in Bonus Room, Anderson Replacement Windows, upgraded Stainless Steel Appliances, New roof in 2022, New HVAC in 2021, New Water Heater and New Refrigerator. All Bedrooms, Baths and Laundry room are downstairs with a Bonus Room over the 2 car garage. You will love to Entertain friends in the spacious living room with Gas Log Fireplace or carry your party outside to the Deck and Patio in your own fenced backyard. The Corner lot allows your guest to use the side yard for extra parking. Seller including a One Year Home Warranty and $3,000 Buyer Incentive.    *Listing Agent has ownership interest in this property.
